    Account An account is an entity (person or company) that applies for or purchases one or more policies from the carrier. Account attributes include years in business, industry code (SIC, NAICS, etc) and nature of ops, FEIN identifier, Bureau (WC) number and business entity type (e.g. individual, corp., partenership, etc.)
